K - The underlying key record type.

EntityScanner<K,E>, Iterable<KeyEntity<K,E>>
public class BaseEntityScanner<K,E>
extends Object
implements EntityScanner<K,E>

Base EntityScanner implementation. This EntityScanner will use an EntityMapper while scanning rows in HBase, and will map each row to KeyEntity pairs.
